reviewText: So glad this was still available. Price was right and 2 thumbs up for seller!

Just before he began his run in Magnum P.I., Tom Selleck guest-starred as the self-assured private eye Lance White in this episode of The Rockford Files. Selleck and Garner have to work together to solve a murder at the annual awards dinner of the United Association of Licensed Investigators.

The clashing styles of the smooth, dashing Selleck and Garner's skeptical everyman made this a fun episode.
